latestIgtvVideos.title: Papacream X Rhea Kapoor
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
IT’S HERE! My first food collab ever! 8 months and so many trials in the making and we are finally able to share our labour of love, nostalgia and goodness: #RheaXPapacream! Food has been my go to happy place these past few months and this was just the most satisfying and exciting project!
I’ve worked hard to put together my dream icecream collection with
@papacream.india 

From a my fave hazelnut cold coffee combination to a the perfect chocolate of childhood memories, from my days of eating the perfect hot fudge sundae on trips to delhi with my cousins to crushing crispy biscuits into a swirl of caramel and buttery cream - this collection will take you on a rollercoaster of nostalgia, yumminess, comfort and happiness!

Now available in Mumbai and Bangalore on www.papacream.com
OR order via Scootsy on Swiggy @scootsyit in Mumbai.

For availability in all other cities please clink on the link in bio!

latestIgtvVideos.title: Meri Wali Home Story
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Growing up with siblings is one of the greatest blessings in life. They are our first best friends and the foes we can't live without. The most beautiful aspect of the sibling relation, however, is that no matter how old you grow, how distant you stay, and how busy or stressed you are, even the thought of being with your sibling(s) in the safety of your house takes all the stress away. It is one of the most refreshing and overwhelming feelings. 

The same is the bond that I have shared with my siblings all through my life. We have been together, from being partners in crime to pillars of strength for each other. @square_yards gave us this beautiful chance to relive our memories and has motivated us to make new ones this Raksha Bandhan.
This was #meriwalihomestory , and you can share yours too on www.squareyards.com
@harshvarrdhankapoor 
#rakhi #rakshabandhan #siblings #siblingbond #sister #brother #squareyards

latestPosts.caption:
From concept to Cannes—witness the journey of Alia Bhatt’s (@aliaabhatt) bespoke jewellery by Malabar Gold & Diamonds, co-created with Rhea Kapoor.

Meticulously handcrafted over 600 man hours, the creation weaves Victorian-era old-cut solitaire diamonds with rustic-finish gold—merging vintage allure with contemporary style.
Each piece is thoughtfully designed to complement Alia’s Cannes debut, blending heritage artistry, Malabar Gold And Diamonds design expertise, and modern elegance.

This is more than a jewellery—a fusion of exquisite precision, design artistry, and iconic style brought to life on the world’s most prestigious red carpet.
